draftinputlines.sty

Add input line numbers to documents.

This package was inspired by Martin Scharrer's question on
tex.stackexchange.
http://tex.stackexchange.com/q/23063/215

Martin himself pointed me towards some of the useful things that make
this package tick. It also makes use of his filehook and currfile
packages.

